==English==

===Noun===
{{wikipediapar|Cephalic disorders}}
# A [[congenital]] disorder involving insufficient division of the [[lobe]]s of the [[brain]] during [[fetus|fetal]] development, resulting in [[skull]] and [[face|facial]] deformities ranging from minor [[cleft lip]] problems to ''[[cyclopia]]'', in which a single eye develops where the nose would normally be.

